{"id":174849,"date":"2023-06-30T02:34:14","date_gmt":"2023-06-29T21:04:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=174849"},"modified":"2023-06-30T16:26:24","modified_gmt":"2023-06-30T10:56:24","slug":"k-vidya","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/k-vidya\/","title":{"rendered":"K Vidya Wiki, Height, Age, Boyfriend, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-174852 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya.jpg\" alt=\"K Vidya\" width=\"300\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya.jpg 382w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya-292x300.jpg 292w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>K Vidya is an Indian former SFI (Students&#8217; Federation of India) leader who is accused of furnishing a fake experience certificate of Maharaja&#8217;s College, Ernakulam, a government college in Kerala, to secure the job at the Malayalam Department of the RGM Government College of Attappady in Palakkad district. She was also a former student at Maharaja&#8217;s College, Ernakulam. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.thenewsminute.com\/article\/former-kerala-sfi-leader-k-vidya-lands-fake-certificate-controversy-here-how-178300\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The News Minute<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce1112e6d2\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce1112e6d2\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/k-vidya\/#WikiBiography\" title=\"Wiki\/Biography\">Wiki\/Biography<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/k-vidya\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/k-vidya\/#Family\" title=\"Family\">Family<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/k-vidya\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/k-vidya\/#Controversies\" title=\"Controversies\">Controversies<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/k-vidya\/#Forged_Experience_Certificate\" title=\"Forged Experience Certificate\">Forged Experience Certificate<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/k-vidya\/#Manipulation_of_the_Reservation_Roster\" title=\"Manipulation of the Reservation Roster\">Manipulation of the Reservation Roster<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/k-vidya\/#FactsTrivia\" title=\"Facts\/Trivia\">Facts\/Trivia<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span>Wiki\/Biography<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>K Vidya hails from Maniyanodi in Thrikaripur, Kasaragod. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/malayalam.samayam.com\/local-news\/kasaragod\/allegations-against-former-sfi-leader-k-vidya\/articleshow\/100800589.cms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Malayalam Samayam<\/a><\/span><\/span> She did graduation in Malayalam from Payyannur College. She was a college union member and SFI activist at Maharaja&#8217;s College and Sanskrit University. Vidya enrolled for PhD at Kalady Sree Sankaracharya Sanskrit University in 2020. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/english.mathrubhumi.com\/news\/kerala\/let-she-prove-her-innocence-dr-bichu-malayil-steps-back-from-guiding-vidya-1.8622367\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Mathru Bhumi<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span>Physical Appearance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Height (approx.):<\/strong> 5&#8242; 4&#8243;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Weight (approx.):<\/strong> 55 kg<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour: <\/strong>Dark Brown<\/p>\n<p><strong>Figure Measurements (approx.): <\/strong>34-28-34<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-174853\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya-1.jpg\" alt=\"K Vidya\" width=\"250\" height=\"553\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya-1.jpg 260w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya-1-136x300.jpg 136w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span>Family<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Not much information regarding her family is available.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span>Career<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>According to her experience certificates, she has previously worked as an assistant professor on a contractual basis from June 2018 to March 2019 and from June 2020 to March 2021 at Maharaja College, Ernakulam. She has also worked at Karinthalam College in Kasaragod from June 2022 to March 2023 as guest faculty.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Controversies\"><\/span>Controversies<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Forged_Experience_Certificate\"><\/span><strong>Forged Experience Certificate<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>According to the reports, Vidya submitted the forged experience documents and certificates while giving the job interview for the position of guest lecturer at the Malayalam Department of the RGM Government College of Attappady in Palakkad district on 2 June 2023. On Wednesday 7 June 2023, the matter gained public attention when the RGM college authorities sent the experience certificate of Vidya to the principal of Maharaja&#8217;s college when they developed doubts related to the authenticity of the certificates. According to reports, Vidya had previously worked at Karinthalam College in Kasaragod from June 2022 to March 2023, utilizing the same forged certificate. The case gained media coverage when another controversy involved PM Arsho, the State Secretary of SFI (Students Federation of India). It was revealed that Arsho&#8217;s mark sheet indicated that he had passed exams at Maharaja&#8217;s College without actually taking them. Arsho, an MA Archaeology student, clarified that he had not written any papers during the third-semester exams, which led to the allegations against him. The authorities of Maharaja College concluded that it was due to a software error at the National Informatics Centre (NIC). The principal of Maharaja College confirmed that Vidya has produced forged documents in the name of the college and confirmed that they have not employed a single person as guest faculty in the Malayalam department for the last 10 years. On this, the authorities of the Maharaja College filed a complaint against Vidya. Ernakulam Central police filed a case against Vidya on the petition filed by the authorities of the Maharaja College where Vidya had been using forged experience documents, stating that she had worked as an assistant professor on a contractual basis in the college from June 2018 to March 2019 and from June 2020 to March 2021.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_174855\" style=\"width: 311px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya-Certificate.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-174855\" class=\"wp-image-174855\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya-Certificate.jpg\" alt=\"K Vidya Certificate\" width=\"301\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya-Certificate.jpg 655w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/K-Vidya-Certificate-253x300.jpg 253w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 301px) 100vw, 301px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-174855\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Copy of K Vidya&#8217;s forged experience certificate from Maharaja College<\/p><\/div>\n<p>According to the FIR reports, the charges registered are Sections 465 (forgery), 468 (forgery for the purpose of cheating), and 471 (using a document or electronic record knowing that it is forged) of the Indian Penal Code. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.thenewsminute.com\/article\/former-kerala-sfi-leader-k-vidya-lands-fake-certificate-controversy-here-how-178300\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The News Minute<\/a><\/span><\/span> <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/timesofindia.indiatimes.com\/city\/kozhikode\/after-15-days-former-sfi-leader-vidya-finally-nabbed\/articleshow\/101175141.cms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Times Of India<\/a><\/span><\/span> The case was later transferred to Agali police station as the RGM College comes under its jurisdiction. On Wednesday 21 June 2023, the police took Vidya into custody from Meppayur in Kozhikode. Vidya was taken from her friend&#8217;s house in Meppayur around 7 pm. The police said that they managed to catch Vidya with the help of mobile phone calls and the tower location of her friends. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[6]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_6\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/timesofindia.indiatimes.com\/city\/kozhikode\/after-15-days-former-sfi-leader-vidya-finally-nabbed\/articleshow\/101175141.cms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Times Of India<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Manipulation_of_the_Reservation_Roster\"><\/span><strong>Manipulation of the Reservation Roster<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>As per the reports, it is found that Kalady Sree Sankaracharya Sanskrit University&#8217;s SC\/ST cell regarding K Vidya&#8217;s PhD admission indicates that the reservation roster was manipulated during the admission process in 2020. The reports also showed the intervention of the vice-chancellor&#8217;s office in the matter. Due to this, Dr Bichu Malayil stepped back from the academic association with K Vidya during the course of her PhD at the university unless Vidya proves herself innocent. As per the reports, Vidya has used her forged experience certificate at the Government Arts and Science College, Kinanoor, Karindalam, Kasaragod to secure the job of guest lecturer. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[7]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_7\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/english.mathrubhumi.com\/news\/kerala\/let-she-prove-her-innocence-dr-bichu-malayil-steps-back-from-guiding-vidya-1.8622367\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Mathru Bhumi<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FactsTrivia\"><\/span>Facts\/Trivia<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The Congress party accused Vidya of using political connections to get the forged documents as she was an SFI activist during her college days at Maharaja College. However, education minister R Bindu claimed that the seal on the certificate was fake and the college has nothing to do with it. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[8]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_8\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/english.mathrubhumi.com\/education\/news\/document-entirely-fake-says-principal-vidya-may-be-arrested-as-police-slap-non-bailable-charges-1.8622036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Mathru Bhumi<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>On the arrest of K Vidya after 15 days of filing the complaint, the police confirmed that she has used the false certificates to beat the senior to secure a job at Karinthalam Government College in Kasaragod. Her competition was with a senior K. Rasitha and she told how having the false documents helped her to secure a job in the college. Out of all the candidates shortlisted for the job, Vidya secured the top rank while Rasitha secure the second. If Vidya wouldn&#8217;t have submitted the fake documents, Rasitha would have secured the job in the college. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_9\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[9]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_9\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onmanorama.com\/news\/kerala\/2023\/06\/29\/fake-experience-certificate-case-k-vidya-wanted-to-beat-senior-in-interview.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Onmaronama<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>As per the sources, K Vidya has made the fake documents on her mobile phone. She created the fake seal and the entire certificate without anyone&#8217;s help. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_10\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[10]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_10\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onmanorama.com\/news\/kerala\/2023\/06\/29\/fake-experience-certificate-case-k-vidya-wanted-to-beat-senior-in-interview.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Onmanorama<\/a><\/span><\/span> The college seal and designation seal was all made using the cam scanner app. The logo of the college was downloaded from Google. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_11\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[11]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_11\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/keralakaumudi.com\/en\/news\/news.php?id=1097414&amp;u=\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Kerala Kaumudi<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>The police were able to retrieve the fake documents from her mobile phone with the help of a cyber cell. As per the reports, the has destroyed all her original forged certificates.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Vidya was earlier arrested by Agali police but was granted bail on certain conditions. However, she was arrested again in the Kasaragod case.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>At the time of the interrogation, Vidya developed uneasiness and was admitted to the hospital. Doctors claimed that it was due to excessive dehydration and that she was not feeling well. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_12\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[12]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_174849_1_12\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.newindianexpress.com\/states\/kerala\/2023\/jun\/24\/former-sfi-leader-k-vidya-feelsuneasiness-during-interrogation-admitted-to-hospital-2587968.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The New Indian Express<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_label_expand_174849_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">References<\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[+]<\/span><span><\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button collapsed\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_174849_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[\u2212]<\/span><\/p><\/div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container_174849_1\" class=\"collapsed\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">References<\/caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_174849_1_1\" class=\"footnote_backlink\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor_174849_1('footnote_plugin_tooltip_174849_1_1');\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>1,<\/a> <a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_174849_1_4\" cl